author: @nuningpurjiati9643
text:
Suara jaenyun very good,ngebass dan doyoung suara tingginya yang aku suka. Lirik lagunya bagus tapi kok sedih ya....
Liriknya: kalau punya perasaan jangan dipendam nanti sesak napas,disampaikan aja ke dia. Ditolak atau tidak itu sudah resiko yang harus ditanggung. Resiko komunikasi pertemanan agak menurun frekuensinya,tapi itu berjalan beberapa waktu aja. Selanjutnya pasti suatu saat dia akan merasakan biasanya komunikasi terus, sekarang kok nggak. Pasti dia akan merindukan komunikasi itu tadi dan akhirnya dia akan menghubungi Anda.
Liriknya sama yg saya alami. Hanya bedanya tidak dipendam tapi disampaikan, agar dia tahu. Memang resikonya sama yang saya sampaikan diatas tadi.Dan akhirnya saya dan suami awalnya teman sekarang jadi pasangan yang bahagia sampai sekarang (22 th).

author: @nandaanandoo
text: DJJ, at least for me, feels like a gift as Jaehyun’s fans. Jaehyun is an all rounder according to SM, but in a group as packed as NCT, he sometimes gets overshadowed. It hurts especially when I saw people undermining his main vocalist status. But in DJJ, not only singing, but he also got to show us his dancing (which is sadly also underrated). We don’t talk enough about his talents, and how all rounder is truly an apt role for him. I’ve been waiting for SM to showcase his talents to their fullest for years. So thank you DJJ for this chance, not only for Jaehyun but also for Doyoung and Jungwoo. I will cherish this unit forever 🫶🏻
